Title: Tropical Cyclone Data R Package
Version: 0.1.0
Author@R: person("Ray", "Fang", email = "fangjiarui2002@outlook.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Leqi", "Tian", email = "lt438@cornell.edu",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: an R package related to the HURDAT Atlantic basin tropical cyclone data (https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/#hurdat). 
    A tropical cyclone is generic term for a strong circulating storm. A tropical storm is a weaker tropical cyclone, and a hurricane is a stronger tropical cyclone..
